  "PackageSlug": "npm/openclaw",
  "Title": "OpenClaw has a Discord `allowFrom` slug-collision authorization bypass",
  "Description": "OpenClaw supports Discord allowlists using either user IDs or names/tags. Name/tag matching depends on slug normalization, so different user tags can collide to the same slug and unintentionally satisfy a name-based allowlist entry.",
